data.description: Welcome to 10923 Bosal Trail. This beautiful two story, 3 bedrooms, 2.5 full baths, game room, large kitchen with island, large family room and separate dining. Ceramic tile throughout downstairs and carpet upstairs. Master bedroom upstairs with full bath, double vanity, separate tub, and shower. Large back yard and front facing a greenbelt. Water softener included. Located off Highway 1604 West, Highway 90, 410 West and Highway 151. Near Lackland Airforce Base, Sea World, Alamo Ranch, and Downtown SA.
